Klarinɛtɩ kɛna hɩlaɣ nakɛyɩ nɛ kaɖaʊ ɖalaɣ lʊʊʊ nɛ kɛwɛ kulukulu ɖaalakɩŋ yɔɔ yee patakɩlɩ-kɛ canʊʊ ɛzɩ lɛɛsɩ yɔ yɔ. Weyi payaɣ-ɩ se Johann Christoph Denner (1655-1707) yɔ,  ɛnʊ lubina-kɛ  Nurambɛrgi tɛtʊ taa pɩnaɣ 1690. 
Ɛlɛ hɩlaɣ nakayɩ kɛ ɛcɔna nɛ ɛsaɣ-kanɛ ɛnʊ. Hɩlaɣ ŋga ɛcɔnaa yɔ, payaɣ-kɛ se luuja yaa tɛyɛ hɩlaɣ yaa ɖɔɖɔ feɖe. 
Hɩlaɣ kanɛ hendu tewu siŋŋŋ taa lɛ, ka-yaʊ taa lɛ, mayaɣ ŋga payaɣ se  si♭ yɔ ŋga pakɩlɩʊ labɩnaʊ tʊmɩyɛ. Hɩsɩ nzɩ payaɣ-sɩ nɔɔ yɔɔ yɔ, sɩ-taa payɩ lɛ klarinɛtɩ kɩlɩʊ wiluu hoŋŋhoŋŋ nɛ kɩwɛna hola ɛzɩ nanaza yɔ nɛ hola  yaa cɛcɛsɩ kiwiwisi cikpesi ɛzɩ looɖo yɔ yaa ɛzɩ wendu masɩ ɛzɩ 45 yɔ.
